data.description: Welcome to the serene Bluffs of Ashley River! This spacious 4-bedroom, 2235 sq ft home is a true gem. The Jamison C plan offers the perfect blend of elegance and functionality. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a boxed ceiling in the master bedroom, adding a touch of grandeur.The kitchen boasts a modern gas range, while enhanced cabinets and crown molding on the first floor elevate the overall aesthetic.The master bedroom, conveniently located on the main level, features a separate tub and shower, ensuring your daily retreat is nothing short of luxurious.Outside, you'll find a peaceful wooded backyard, providing both privacy and tranquility. A wooden fence encloses the back yard, making it ideal for pets and gatherings.But the charm doesn't end there - step onto the screened back porch and soak in the beauty of your surroundings. This home is a haven of comfort and style, ready to welcome you home.
